<h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<p>ParsedownExtended adds the ability to use diagrams in your markdown, by adding support for <a href="https://www.chartjs.org">ChartJS</a> and <a href="https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/">Mermaid</a>. By looking out for code related to diagrams and avoid it so it doesn‚Äùt get manipulated. To use the function you will have to include their .js files in your project.</p>

